thread.title: Francys
thread.title_full: LIGHTHOUSE Dental Cobourg reviewed by Francys

author: Francys
title: Francys
text: The whole office is full of cheerful professional staff, prices are good, and the best part: they have never cause me any pain. I always thought having ones teeth cleaned was supposed to hurt. But they changed my mind. They didn't hurt my gums. The second I felt any discomfort the hygienist used some numbing gel. Now my gums don't hurt and my teeth are food as new.
